query:
INSERT INTO projects (
                    id,
                    name,
                    git_repo_path,
                    setup_script,
                    dev_script,
                    cleanup_script,
                    copy_files,
                    release_ports_on_completion
                ) VALUES (
                    $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8
                )
                RETURNING id as "id!: Uuid",
                          name,
                          git_repo_path,
                          setup_script,
                          dev_script,
                          cleanup_script,
                          copy_files,
                          release_ports_on_completion,
                          remote_project_id as "remote_project_id: Uuid",
                          created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                          updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
